Name: Alasdair Mhic Cholla Ghasda

!   Emi
1. Alasdair Mhic o ho Cholla Ghasda o ho
!                           C                  D  Emi
   As do laimh-s' gun o ho Earbainn tapaidh trom eile.
!     Emi
R: Chall eile bho chall a ho ro Chall eile bho chall a ho ro
!               C              Ami              D      Emi
   Chall eile huraibh i chall a ho ro 'S haoi ho trom eile.
2. As do laimh-s' gun o ho
   Earbainn tapaidh o ho
   Mharbhadh Tighearne o ho
   Ach-nam Breac leat trom eile.
R:
3. 'S ged's beag mi fhein o ho
   Bhuail mi ploc air o ho
   Chuala mi'n de o ho
   Sgeul nach b'ait leam trom eile.
R:
4. Chaula mi'n de o ho
   Sgeul nach b'ait leam o ho
   Glaschu a bhith o ho
   Dol'na lasair trom eile.
R:
5. Glaschu a bhith o ho
   Dol'na lasair o ho
   'S Obair-Dheathain o ho
   'N deidh a chreachadh trom eile.
R:
